patients with a life expectancy of a few weeks and a Karnofsky Performance 
Status ≤40. Factor structure and concurrent validity of PDI and correlations 
between dignity and anxious and depressive symptomatology, quality of life, 
demoralization, personal coping styles, spiritual well-being, and spiritual 
